theorem unop {A B X Y : «expr ᵒᵖ» C} {i : «expr ⟶ » A B} {p : «expr ⟶ » X Y} (h : has_lifting_property i p) :
    has_lifting_property p.unop i.unop :=
  ⟨fun f g sq => by
    rw [comm_sq.has_lift.iff_op]
    simp only [quiver.hom.op_unop]
    infer_instance⟩
#align unop unop
